        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are an expert video script writer for YouTube Shorts.\n\nVideo Title: {{ $('Get row to process').item.json.idea }}\nVideo Description: {{ $('Get row to process').item.json.caption }}\nVisual Style: {{ $('Get row to process').item.json.character_style_prompt }}\nNarration Tone: {{ $('Get row to process').item.json.channel_style_prompt }}\n\nCreate a script for a 60-second vertical video (YouTube Shorts format).\n\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON array of 5 scene objects. No markdown, no explanation.\n\nEach scene object must have:\n- voiceText: voiceover text for this scene (2 sentences, 11-15 words each)\n- visualPrompt: detailed image generation prompt for this scene matching the visual style above\n\nMake it flow as one continuous philosophical story. Do not use double quotes inside text values."
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.8,
